  "prompt": "Where do I get all episodes of dragon ball Kai in English?",
  "response": "Dragon Ball Kai, also known as Dragon Ball Z Kai, has been released in its entirety and can be found through various legal streaming services and retail platforms. Here are a few places you can check:\n\n1. **Funimation**: Funimation often has the rights to many Dragon Ball series and you can stream episodes of Dragon Ball Z Kai directly through their service.\n\n2. **Crunchyroll**: Crunchyroll might offer Dragon Ball Z Kai for streaming depending on licensing agreements. It's worth checking their platform.\n\n3. **Amazon Prime Video**: Episodes and seasons of Dragon Ball Z Kai might be available for purchase or streaming on Amazon Prime Video.\n\n4. **Hulu**: Hulu may also offer the series, given their extensive library of anime.\n\n5. **DVD/Blu-ray**: You can purchase physical copies of Dragon Ball Z Kai on DVD or Blu-ray through online retailers like Amazon, Walmart, or local stores that specialize in media.\n\n6. **Other Streaming Services**: Platforms like Google Play, iTunes, and Netflix occasionally have agreements to stream popular anime, including Dragon Ball Z Kai.\n\nMake sure to use legal and official sources for streaming and purchasing to support the creators and distributors.",
